description:
Kate works through some negative body image thoughts and Doree begins to question time when she realizes both of Henry’s birthdays have been during the pandemic. Then, listeners let Doree know that Call My Agent is not actually over, ask about an interesting aging myth, and call in just to express feeling joy.


  • To leave a voicemail or text for a future episode, reach us at 781-591-0390. You can also email the podcast at forever35podcast@gmail.com.
